Add pattern difficulty estimator with 1-10 scoring and radial gauge

Enhanced the DifficultyEstimator with a comprehensive scoring algorithm
analyzing 6 factors: unique fabrics, total piece count, smallest piece
size, curved seams, complex points/intersections, and piece density per
square foot. Displays as a radial SVG gauge with colored segments and
an expandable "Why this rating" breakdown showing each factor's
contribution. Updated PatternResults difficulty labels to match the
new 1-10 scale (1-3 Beginner, 4-6 Intermediate, 7-8 Advanced, 9-10
Expert).

